AboutMe:
James Chorlton is a software developer based in Bristol, UK. He primarily develops software for the legal and healthcare industries (MOJ RTA/ELPL Portal, Case Management, PI Management, Patient Management etc) along with private contract work in other industries.

Along with software development James is a amature (rather!) photographer, lapsed computer gamer and westie owner!

A Bristol Geek is his ranting ground, and where he likes to try and show off bits of photography. You can find him around the web under the name jamesakadamingo, or on twitter @jamesakadamingo
